Continue converting remaining targets
8. Phase 2 – Decoupling (Future State)
After all targets are converted to Gradle:
We will move into decoupling phase.
Goals:
Move all shared/common components to Artifactory
Break dependencies between targets
Ensure each build produces its own independent artifact
9. Target Architecture
The final system will:
